name      url           verb     desc.

_____________________________________________________

index     /dog           GET      Display a List of all Dogs
new      /dog/new        GET      Display form to make a new Dog
create    /dog           POST     Add new dog to Database
show     /dog/:id        GET      Show info. about one dog
edit     /dog/:id/edit   GET      Show edit for one dog
Update   /dog/:id        PUT      Update a particular dog and then redirect someWhere
Destroy  /dog/:id        DELETE   Delete a particular dog and then redirect someWhere